message.content:
Ecco una landing page HTML/CSS/JS single-file per un negozio di programmazione AI in stile cyberpunk, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Code Emporium • Cyberpunk</title>
    <!-- Font futuristico -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: #0a0f1e;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            color: #d0f0ff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, #1f2b3a 0%, #0a0f1e 80%);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(10, 15, 30, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            border: 2px solid #00f7ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px #00f7ff44, inset 0 0 20px #00f7ff22;
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        /* cyberpunk heading */
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            color: #f0f8ff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #00f7ff, 0 0 30px #0077ff, 0 0 60px #0044ff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .sub-glow {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #b0e0ff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #00f7ff55;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px #00aaff;
        }

        .grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .card {
            background: #121827dd;
            border: 1px solid #33ffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            flex: 1 1 280px;
            max-width: 320px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00ffff33, inset 0 0 10px #00ffff22;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: #ff00ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px #ff00ff55;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #aaffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 6px #00ffff;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffd700;
            text-shadow: 0 0 12px #ffbb00;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .desc {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #b0d0e0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .btn-neon {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #00f7ff;
            color: #00f7ff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .btn-neon:hover {
            background: #00f7ff;
            color: #0a0f1e;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px #00f7ff, 0 0 60px #00aaff;
        }

        /* modulo contatti */
        .contact-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 2px dashed #ff00ff55;
            padding-top: 30px;
        }

        .contact-inner {
            max-width: 580px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #0e1424dd;
            border: 1px solid #ff66ff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 30px 25px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px #ff00ff33;
        }

        .contact-inner h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #f0aaff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff00ff;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #b0f0ff;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            background: #1a1f2e;
            border: 1px solid #33ffff;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #e0f0ff;
            outline: none;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            border-color: #ff00ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff00ff44;
        }

        textarea {
            min-height: 100px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            background: #ff00ff;
            border: none;
            color: #0a0f1e;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            width: 100%;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff00ff88;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background: #ff33ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px #ff00ff, 0 0 80px #ff00ff88;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        /* popup */
        .popup-overlay {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: #000000aa;
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .popup-box {
            background: #121827;
            border: 3px solid #00f7ff;
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 40px 50px;
            max-width: 420px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 0 60px #00f7ff66;
            animation: flicker 0.3s;
        }

        .popup-box h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #aaffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px #00ffff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .popup-box p {
            color: #b0e0ff;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .popup-close {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #ff00ff;
            color: #ff00ff;
            padding: 8px 30px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .popup-close:hover {
            background: #ff00ff;
            color: #0a0f1e;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px #ff00ff;
        }

        @keyframes flicker {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #667788;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .container { padding: 20px 15px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>⚡ AI CODE EMPORIUM</h1>
        <div class="sub-glow">✦ cyberpunk programming • neural shop ✦</div>

        <!-- prodotti -->
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>NEURAL ENGINE</h3>
                <div class="price">$499</div>
                <div class="desc">Predictive AI core • TensorFlow 4.0<br>Edge deployment ready</div>
                <button class="btn-neon" onclick="alert('🔧 Aggiunto al sistema neurale')">ACQUISTA</button>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>DEEP SYNTAX</h3>
                <div class="price">$799</div>
                <div class="desc">Compiler AI • NLP • code generation<br>Zero-shot reasoning</div>
                <button class="btn-neon" onclick="alert('🔧 Modulo Deep Syntax inizializzato')">ACQUISTA</button>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>CYBER DREAM</h3>
                <div class="price">$1,299</div>
                <div class="desc">Full-stack AI dev kit • 10 models<br>API cybernetiche</div>
                <button class="btn-neon" onclick="alert('🔧 Cyber Dream installato')">ACQUISTA</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- modulo contatti -->
        <div class="contact-section">
            <div class="contact-inner">
                <h2>📡 CONTACT NODE</h2>
                <form id="contactForm">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">◈ NOME / ID</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="il tuo tag" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">◈ EMAIL / CYBERBOX</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="nome@dominio" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message">◈ MESSAGGIO</label>
                        <textarea id="message" placeholder="Richiedi un modello AI, assistenza o connessione..." required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">◈ INVIA RICHIESTA</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer>✦ AI-2077 • tutti i dati sono criptati con firma quantica ✦</footer>
    </div>

    <!-- popup -->
    <div class="popup-overlay" id="popupOverlay">
        <div class="popup-box">
            <h3>✔ RICHIESTA INVIATA</h3>
            <p>Il tuo messaggio è entrato nella rete neurale.<br>Risposta entro 2.4 nanosecondi.</p>
            <button class="popup-close" id="closePopup">CHIUDI</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        (function() {
            const form = document.getElementById('contactForm');
            const popup = document.getElementById('popupOverlay');
            const closeBtn = document.getElementById('closePopup');

            // mostra popup
            function showPopup() {
                popup.style.display = 'flex';
            }

            // nascondi popup
            function hidePopup() {
                popup.style.display = 'none';
            }

            // gestione invio form
            form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();

                // piccola validazione base
                const name = document.getElementById('name').value.trim();
                const email = document.getElementById('email').value.trim();
                const message = document.getElementById('message').value.trim();

                if (!name || !email || !message) {
                    alert('⚠️ Compila tutti i campi, operatore.');
                    return;
                }

                // simula invio e mostra popup
                showPopup();

                // reset opzionale
                form.reset();
            });

            // chiusura popup
            closeBtn.addEventListener('click', hidePopup);

            // click fuori dal popup? (opzionale)
            popup.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                if (e.target === popup) {
                    hidePopup();
                }
            });

            // tasto ESC per chiudere
            document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
                if (e.key === 'Escape' && popup.style.display === 'flex') {
                    hidePopup();
                }
            });
        })();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

### Caratteristiche principali

- **Stile cyberpunk** con colori neon, bordi luminosi, sfondo scuro e font futuristico "Orbitron".
- **Tre prodotti** in griglia con pulsanti "Acquista" (simulano aggiunta al sistema).
- **Modulo contatti** completo (nome, email, messaggio) con validazione base.
- **Popup JS** che appare all'invio del modulo con il testo "Richiesta inviata" e pulsante di chiusura.
- **Codice compatto e valido** in un unico file HTML, con CSS e JS integrati.

Il popup si attiva solo dopo aver compilato tutti i campi del modulo e cliccato "Invia richiesta". Puoi chiuderlo con il pulsante "CHIUDI", cliccando fuori dalla finestra o premendo ESC.
